                <p class="mb-4">Our mission is to make healthy eating accessible and enjoyable for everyone. We believe that the journey to a healthier lifestyle begins with what you eat, and we're here to support you every step of the way.</p>
                <p class="mb-4">Thank you for choosing Fruitables. We look forward to serving you with the best nature has to offer.</p>
                <a href="@Url.Action("Index", "Products")" class="btn btn-primary rounded-pill px-4 py-3">Explore Our Products</a>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-6">
                <img src="~/img/fruite-item-5.jpg" class="img-fluid rounded" alt="About Fruitables">
